Package: MEHAHO
Title: Use MEHA and LV-HVA to solve some hyper-parameter selection problems.
Version: 0.1.1
Authors@R: 
    c(
    person("Pengyu", "Zhu", , "12332853@mail.sustceh.edu.cn", role = c("aut", "cre")),
    person("Zhiheng", "Tan", , "12111603@mail.sustech.edu.cn", role = "aut")
    )
Description: A R package to handle with hyper-parameter optimization in 
    machine learning methods including elastic net, sparse group Lasso, low rank 
    matrix completion and SVM. Please refer to the listed literature for the specific model.
    We provide the option to automatically adjust MEHA (LV-HBA) hyper-parameters using simulated annealing algorithms.
